{{see|Transference}}
==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# The act of [[transferring]] or the fact of being [[transferred]].
# {{psychology}} The process by which [[emotion]]s and [[desire]]s, originally associated with one person, such as a [[parent]], are [[unconsciously]] shifted to another.

